               <head type="stepTitle" xml:lang="en">Create a wordlist</head>
               <desc type="definition" xml:lang="en">Creating a wordlist is a basic functionality of a concordance program.
                 After uploading your own corpus or selecting an already available corpus usually the first step consists
                 in looking at the most frequent items of the corpus. Select the minimum and maximum frequency.
                 You can also apply a stoplist if you wish to filter the terms.</desc>
